data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS - Seller(s) to Offer $5,000 towards Rate Buydown or Buyer Closing Costs - Spacious and inviting 3BR/2BA home built in 1987, boasting 1950 SQFT – one of, if not the, largest home in the neighborhood. HVAC approximately 5 years old, a 2011 roof, and black stainless steel appliances enhance the home's modernity. The oversized kitchen, remodeled in 2018, features quartz countertops, a large island, Lanai Access and newer wood tile floors. The main bathroom was remodeled in 2015 and the large master bathroom features a double vanity. The residence has great potential and charm. Enjoy seamless indoor-outdoor living with 3 glass sliding doors connecting the home to the expansive pool/lanai area. No HOA fees. This Holiday gem is perfect for entertaining and showcases one of the area's finest kitchens.
